INSERT INTO `information` VALUES (1,'都怪英国没蓝翔 挖掘机被困在海里回不来了','挖掘机下海','/files/54c4f1ffcee9d1dd7ac79f5d1c3bb42b.jpeg',6,'<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">近日，英国苏塞克斯海岸线出现喜感一幕：一辆挖掘机被困在海中，被水淹没，不知所措。直到下一个涨潮日之前，别想让它回到岸上了。</p><p class=\"detailPic\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p2.ifengimg.com/a/2017_14/6ea694e318fbcce_size41_w620_h389.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"201\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在英国著名的苏塞克斯海岸线上，当地的工程人员正计划热火朝天的干一件大事——他们要利用这海风来做清洁能源，建一个风场来给这个城市发电。工程师们都充满了干劲，首先在这海滩边划了有三个纽约曼哈顿岛大小的地盘，预计要花掉13亿英镑，还为这个项目购置了一个大约85万英镑的挖掘机。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">当然这个挖掘机是重头戏，除了普通的挖掘机该有的部件以外，它还为此专门设计成钻井平台那样，能够稳稳地扎在海滩边的支架，这样就能固定住挖掘机不被海风吹倒了。有这样的挖掘机在，那些工程师们都自信的表示，明年我们就能让风场发电！</p><p class=\"detailPic\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p2.ifengimg.com/a/2017_14/6146d4c05cae660_size40_w620_h353.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"182\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">不过现在看来，这个工期得延迟了。为什么呢？</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">有一天居民们发现，这挖掘机不应该在岸边挖土吗？怎么突然跑到海里去了？</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">难道是在挖海水？或者是最近遇到什么节日，这群有趣的工程师在弄什么行为艺术？</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这帮工程师其实也不明不白的，当他们还在挖掘机里研究方案时，这突然就——涨潮了！</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">潮水很快遍淹没了挖掘机底部，连固定它的支架都慢慢没过，就剩驾驶室和手臂还能看得见。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">咋的啦？淹没进去了，开出来不就完了呗，再简单不过的事儿，蓝翔月考而已。可是英国没蓝翔啊！这帮工程师根本没法把这大家伙开回岸边啊！</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">工程师们只好登上一个小船，从被淹没的挖掘机里面逃了出来。之后，又一批工作人员跑上去，把这挖掘机里600升的柴油给抽了出来，以免污染海水。不过还好这挖掘机是经过特殊设计的，它早已牢牢地扎在了地上，涨潮退潮倒是不会把它给弄走。为了安全起见，一艘工地上的警卫船开到附近，给周围放上了浮标以作警示。</p><p class=\"detailPic\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p3.ifengimg.com/a/2017_14/18488dc0975aee6_size57_w748_h546.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"234\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">现在这帮工程师们只好等着下一次退潮，等挖掘机履带露出来以后再开会去了。可到现在，两个星期过去了，退潮还遥遥无期。</p><p><br/></p>','2017-04-06 20:07:03','2017-04-24 05:49:41',NULL);
